snippet.title: Daley Thompson's Decathlon on the ZX Spectrum
snippet.description:
The first few events of the legendary Daley Thompson Decathlon by Ocean Software on the ZX Spectrum.

I can't remember how to do the high jump - so if anyone can let me know how to do it then great!

I reviewed this game at http://zxspectrumgames.blogspot.com/2009/05/zx-spectrum-games-daley-thompsons.html if you're interested

Cheers all.
